CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FA man who photographed and filmed
OL,8,Fwomen through their windows in north
OL,9,FLondon has admitted a number of counts
OL,10,Fof voyeurism.
OL,12,FAnthony Durkan, 35, of Corporation
OL,13,FStreet, Islington, pleaded guilty to
OL,14,F19 counts of voyeurism at Highbury
OL,15,FCorner Magistrates' Court this
OL,16,Fafternoon (July 21).
OL,18,FHe had previously admitted to seven
OL,19,Fother voyeurism charges in March this
OL,20,Fyear, bringing his total counts to 26.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
