OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FPolice found Durkan had 162 videos and
OL,8,Fnearly a hundred photos of women on
OL,9,Fhis phone - all of whom looked to be
OL,10,Funaware they were being watched.
OL,12,FAn investigstion into Durkan was
OL,13,Flaunched earlier this year after
OL,14,Fpolice received a report from a woman
OL,15,Fof a man repeatedly attending her home
OL,16,Fin Islington and filming through her
OL,17,Fwindows during the early hours of the
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FShe had been told by her neighbour,
OL,8,Fwho had witnessed a man dressed
OL,9,Fentirely in black and wearing a
OL,10,Fbalaclava walk towards her house.
OL,12,FHe was seen holding his mobile phone
OL,13,Fup to windows, seemingly recording
OL,14,Finside, before walking away. These
OL,15,Fincidents were captured on the
OL,16,Fneighbour's doorbell camera.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FWeeks later, in March 2026, officers
OL,8,Fwere called to another address in
OL,9,FIslington, after a woman reported that
OL,10,Fshe had also spotted a man recording
OL,11,Fher through her window.
OL,13,FDurkan was arrested during a planned
OL,14,Fpatrol of the area on Wednesday, 25
OL,15,FMarch.
OL,17,FA plainclothed officer watched Durkan
OL,18,Fapproach the house and carry out the
OL,19,Fsame pattern of behaviour captured in
OL,20,Fearlier evidence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FFollowing the arrest, Durkan has five
OL,8,Fadditional mobile devices and a small
OL,9,Fcamera seized.
OL,11,FThe women who initially reported the
OL,12,Fvoyeurism offences, as well as an
OL,13,Fadditional victim identified through
OL,14,Fanalysis of Durkan's devices, continue
OL,15,Fto receive dedicated support from
OL,16,Fspecially trained officers.
OL,18,FHowever, police believe a number of
OL,19,Fvictims are yet to be identified.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
