OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FThey are particularly keen to hear
OL,8,Ffrom women in Islington and north
OL,9,FLondon between January 2020 and March
OL,10,F2026 who may have noticed unusual
OL,11,Factivity around their home,
OL,12,Fparticularly at night or in the early
OL,13,Fhours of the morning.
OL,15,FPeople are also asked to report
OL,16,Fsuspicious behaviour, such as someone
OL,17,Flingering near residential properties,
OL,18,Flooking through windows, or using a
OL,19,Fphone or camera.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
