OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Gemma Alger,
OL,8,Fwhose team led the investigation,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Durkan's offending represented
OL,10,Fa serious and sustained course of
OL,11,Fpredatory behaviour, deliberately
OL,12,Ftargeting women who were entirely
OL,13,Funaware they were being filmed,
OL,14,Fwithout their consent and in the
OL,15,Fprivacy of their own homes.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
