OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784843301
OL,3,CVoyeur caught on doorbell camera
OL,4,Cadmits filming women through their
OL,5,Cwindows
OL,7,F"I want to thank the women who had the
OL,8,Fcourage to come forward and report
OL,9,FDurkan's crimes. Their reports,
OL,10,Fsupported by witnesses and swift
OL,11,Finvestigative work, enabled officers
OL,12,Fto act decisively and arrest Durkan
OL,13,Fduring a proactive patrol.
OL,15,F"This conviction reflects the severity
OL,16,Fof these crimes and means a dangerous
OL,17,Findividual has been brought to
OL,18,Fjustice, preventing further harm to
OL,19,Fwomen."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@GO]
